- D: On the contrary signals contradiction, yet the sentence agrees with the scholars.', 'Is the last sentence opposing the scholars or restating their point more plainly?', 'Expression of Ideas', 'Transitions', 'reading_writing', 'expression', 'TRA', NULL, 'hard', false, 'SAT', 'multiple_choice', true, true, 'scholaris_ai', '{"generator":"scholaris_ai_v1","model":"gemma-4-26b-a4b-it","original":true,"explanation_v2":true}'::jsonb, now(), now())
